### 1. **AI-Powered Discovery & Personalization**
* **Multimodal AI “Budtender”**
  * Voice and text input: Users can ask questions naturally: “Show me the best indica for sleep that ships near me,” or “Teach me how to make hash at home.”
  * Image recognition: Users can snap a pic of a strain, product, or accessory and get info, reviews, or sourcing options.
  * Smart recommendations: Tracks user behavior, preferences, purchase history, and even “vibe” to suggest products automatically.
* **Demand-Sensing & Marketing**
  * AI monitors trends worldwide: what’s trending on social, what people are searching for, and dynamically adjusts what to highlight.
  * Automated marketing campaigns: Sends push notifications, emails, or even in-app recommendations, all generated in real-time.
  * Upselling & cross-selling: Suggests complementary products (“If you bought this bong, you might want these custom screens or grinders”).
